Package sorcer.core.provider.rendezvous

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RendezvousBean
    ServiceBean - The SORCER superclass of service components of ServiceProvider.
    ServiceConcatenator
    ServiceJobber - The SORCER rendezvous service provider that manages coordination for executing mograms using service providers that form a dynamic service federation as specified signatures of component mograms.
    ServiceJobber
    ServiceJobber - The SORCER rendezvous service provider that provides coordination for executing mograms using directly (PUSH) service providers.
    ServiceModeler
    ServiceModler - The SORCER rendezvous service provider that manages coordination for executing service models using its service signatures to create a dynamic federation of collaborating providers.
    ServiceRendezvous
    ServiceJobber - The SORCER rendezvous service provider that provides coordination for executing mograms using directly (PUSH) service providers.
    ServiceSpacer
    ServiceSpacer - The SORCER rendezvous service provider that provides coordination for executing mograms using JavaSpace from which provides PULL mograms to be executed.
